{"tid":619706,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"利記破大巴單野 曼城真係好有風度","createTime":"2018-04-07T02:11:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T02:50:39.000Z","uid":7715,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"609df6253c7fd6fbe0545bcc31b2adbbe843f156","tid":619706,"uid":7715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T02:11:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/onesport/cps/624/cpsprodpb/8430/production/_100704833_city-bottle.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fonesport%2Fcps%2F624%2Fcpsprodpb%2F8430%2Fproduction%2F_100704833_city-bottle.jpg&h=6f3d87d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPep Guardiola<br />\n<br />\n&quot;The officers and stewards are there to protect the public and keep them safe. It is disappointing to see that a number of people behaved in this appalling way.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Normally when the police know it is going to happen, they tried to avoid it from happening,&quot; <br />\n<br />\n&quot;We come here to play football and I don't understand this kind of situation.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;The bus is destroyed but I did not expect a prestigious club like Liverpool doing this kind of thing. It is not Liverpool, it is the people, maybe one, two or three, but hopefully it does not happen again.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nDe Bruyne <br />\n<br />\n&quot;It was OK, I don't mind supporters doing that - I've had it a couple of times for my team and it's a nice feeling.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;I am fine with it as long as no-one gets hurt. It doesn't change anything [for the players]. As long as you keep the violence down, there's nothing wrong with it.&quot;"},{"pid":"19471779341f7f90f7d52557eebf06da32ddfe63","tid":619706,"uid":7715,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T02:13:44.000Z","msg":"中文版<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.images.express.co.uk/img/dynamic/67/590x/Liverpool-man-City-Jordan-Henderson-941542.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.images.express.co.uk%2Fimg%2Fdynamic%2F67%2F590x%2FLiverpool-man-City-Jordan-Henderson-941542.jpg&h=53e18548&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n瓜迪奧拉<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;官員和管理人員在那裡保護公眾並保證他們的安全。看到一些人以這種令人震驚的方式行事，這令人失望。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;通常當警方知道會發生時，他們試圖避免它發生，&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我們來這裡踢足球，我不了解這種情況。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;公共汽車被摧毀了，但我沒有想到像利物浦這樣的著名俱樂部做這種事情，這不是利物浦，而是人民，也許是一，二，三，但希望它不會再發生。<br />\n<br />\n德布魯恩<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;沒問題，我不介意這樣做的支持者 - 我已經為我的球隊多次嘗試過，這是一種不錯的感覺。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;只要沒有人受到傷害，我就沒有問題，這對球員沒有任何影響，只要你保持暴力，就沒有問題。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"d0ed11c3966831dc228e0611d7873aff55525c3c","tid":619706,"uid":39065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T02:14:50.000Z","msg":"他首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"021689e3ca2a06425cbee604471812fbdea221f9","tid":619706,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T02:15:10.000Z","msg":"也許是一，二，三<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 哥狗有上高登"},{"pid":"48b360d8a35dd2ce081ec682bdfa93e40d011213","tid":619706,"uid":12911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T02:16:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中文版<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.images.express.co.uk/img/dynamic/67/590x/Liverpool-man-City-Jordan-Henderson-941542.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.images.express.co.uk%2Fimg%2Fdynamic%2F67%2F590x%2FLiverpool-man-City-Jordan-Henderson-941542.jpg&h=53e18548&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n瓜迪奧拉<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;官員和管理人員在那裡保護公眾並保證他們的安全。看到一些人以這種令人震驚的方式行事，這令人失望。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;通常當警方知道會發生時，他們試圖避免它發生，&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我們來這裡踢足球，我不了解這種情況。<br />\n<br />\n&ldq